      "pan style=\" font-size:20px;\">教材中令：Tv=Tm</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin"
      "-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:20px;\">上图中PI控制"
      "器：Kp为Tm时，KI为1时传递函数为(Tms+1)/s</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:"
      "0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:20px;\">这个传递函数可转化"
      "为状态空间形式：</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -"
      "qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:20px;\">num=[Tm 1]; %Tm具体化，例如为12.345</span"
      "></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; tex"
      "t-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:20px;\">den=[1 0];</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-botto"
      "m:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:20px;\""
      ">sys=tf(num,den)</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -"
      "qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:20px;\">[A,B,C,D]=tf2ss(num,den)</span></p>\n<p s"
      "tyle=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0p"
      "x;\"><span style=\" font-size:20px;\">那么A=0, B=1, C=1, D=Tm。（Tm=12.345）</span></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:"
      "0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\""
      " font-size:20px;\">也可转化为离散系统：[Ad,Bd,Cd,Dd]=c2dm(Ac,Bc,Cc,Dc,Tc)。 Tc为离散系统采样时间。</span></p></b"
      "ody></html>"
